Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.84,0:01:28.48,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}油断できない この事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:29.23,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur10\c&H187EF0&\3c&H0304F3&\pos(251,694)}Good luck
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:34.25,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}究極の選択は 永遠のトラウマ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.43,0:01:37.09,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}勝ち負けじゃない 綺麗事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.71,0:01:37.76,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur10\c&H187EF0&\3c&H0304F3&\pos(249,698)}I know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:39.95,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}励ましてくれて ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:40.65,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur10\c&H187EF0&\3c&H0304F3&\pos(289,692)}Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:42.83,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}最後には 自分なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:44.61,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}覚悟決めなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.61,0:01:47.81,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}気になるSuggestion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.81,0:01:53.54,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}理屈は時々無力で ジレンマ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.69,0:01:58.55,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}流されてみてもいいのかも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:02.10,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}運命が 回り出す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:05.68,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}出たとこ勝負で始めるの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:10.53,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}心の準備のあるなしは 待ってくれない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.53,0:02:13.47,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}輝いて ここ一番
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.47,0:02:17.07,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}自分の直感を信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:19.60,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}受け取った miracle rush
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:24.93,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10\fad(0,200)}今最高の奇跡に乗り込め
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:07.71,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}闪耀吧 这里最强
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.71,0:01:11.08,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}相信自己的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:13.97,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}收下了 miracle rush
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.97,0:01:18.87,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10\fad(0,500)}现在就去创造奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.98,0:01:25.52,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不是开玩笑 你明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.31,0:01:26.55,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur10\c&H187EF0&\3c&H0304F3&\pos(968,16)}You know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.84,0:01:28.48,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}这种事情 可不能大意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:29.23,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur10\c&H187EF0&\3c&H0304F3&\pos(964,22)}Good luck
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:34.25,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}最后的选择是心中永远的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.43,0:01:37.09,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}无关胜负 说得好听
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.71,0:01:37.76,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur10\c&H187EF0&\3c&H0304F3&\pos(968,16)}I know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:39.95,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}能够鼓励我 非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:40.65,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur10\c&H187EF0&\3c&H0304F3&\pos(968,16)}Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:42.83,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}最后还是要靠自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:44.61,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不做好觉悟可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.61,0:01:47.81,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}这是深得我心的小建议
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.81,0:01:53.54,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}道理有时并不管用 进退两难
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.69,0:01:58.55,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}顺其自然或许更好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:02.10,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}命运不停轮回
